OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of all 18 charges in his
OL,8,Fhistorical sex offences trial and told
OL,9,Fto expect a lengthly prison sentence.
OL,11,FThe prosecution case, set out before a
OL,12,Fjury of seven men and five women at
OL,13,FNewry Crown Court, was that the former
OL,14,FDUP Leader had sexually assaulted two
OL,15,Fwomen when they were children.
OL,17,FHe has been remanded into custody and
OL,18,Fplaced on the sex offenders' register.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FThe two women, who both gave evidence
OL,7,Fduring the four-week trial, were known
OL,8,Fas Complainants A and B to protect
OL,9,Ftheir identities.
OL,11,FDonaldson was found guilty of 10
OL,12,Fcharges relating to Complainant B, the
OL,13,Folder of the two women, including one
OL,14,Fcount of rape and nine of indecent
OL,15,Fassault, dating from 1985 to 1991.
OL,17,FHe had denied four charges of indecent
OL,18,Fassault and four of gross indecency
OL,19,Frelating to Complainant A, dating from
OL,20,F1999 to 2008. However, the jury
OL,21,Freturned guilty verdicts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FEleanor Donaldson, who faced a trial
OL,7,Fof the facts and did not participate
OL,8,Fin the proceedings on mental health
OL,9,Fgrounds, was found to have aided and
OL,10,Fabetted his crimes.
OL,12,FHer trial of facts tested the evidence
OL,13,Fbut could not result in a criminal
OL,14,Fconviction.
OL,16,FAfter deliberating for just over 10
OL,17,Fhours, the jury returned to the
OL,18,Fcourtroom just after lunch on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FAt 2.15pm Donaldson was asked to stand
OL,7,Fas the court clerk asked the foreman
OL,8,Fof the jury to read the verdicts.
OL,9,FAfter the verdicts were delivered,
OL,10,FJudge Paul Ramsey expressed his
OL,11,F"gratitude and thanks" to the jury.
OL,13,FBefore they left the room, the jury
OL,14,Fmembers were extended exemptions from
OL,15,Fjury service for life.
OL,17,FThe evidence heard by jury during four-
OL,18,Fweek trial of Sir Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
