OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FProsecution barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,7,FKC then confirmed that victim impact
OL,8,Fstatements would be prepared ahead of
OL,9,Fsentencing.
OL,11,FThe judge said there would inevitably
OL,12,Fbe a "lengthy sentence of
OL,13,Fimprisonment". Donaldson was remanded
OL,14,Finto custody and showed no emotion as
OL,15,Fhe was led from the court.
OL,17,FThere will be a review hearing on
OL,18,FSeptember 11 before a sentencing
OL,19,Fhearing later in the month.
OL,26,@tD@FOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/24
