OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FWhen prosecution barrister Rosemary
OL,7,FWalsh KC initially addressed the jury
OL,8,Flast month, she said the ex-MP had
OL,9,Fsubjected the two women to "difficult
OL,10,Fand traumatic incidents" when they
OL,11,Fwere children.
OL,13,FComplainant A was the first witness
OL,14,Fcalled in the trial. She claimed that
OL,15,Fshe had first been abused when of
OL,16,Fprimary school age.
OL,18,FShe told the jury of one incident
OL,19,Fwhere she claimed Donaldson had used a
OL,20,Flight, possibly a torch, to look at
OL,21,Fher "private parts".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@XO]}D@EOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FComplainant A said she told Eleanor
OL,7,FDonaldson about the alleged incident.
OL,9,FShe told the court: "I knew by the
OL,10,Flook on her face she knew I was
OL,11,Ftelling the truth... once she
OL,12,Fidentified I was telling the truth,
OL,13,Fshe did nothing about it."
OL,15,FComplainant A told the court that
OL,16,Fanother incident where she claimed the
OL,17,Fformer politician had put his tongue
OL,18,Fin her mouth had been "laughed off" by
OL,19,Fboth the Donaldsons.
OL,26,@qD@UOUuD@ZO]zD@WOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FShe also claimed he had touched her
OL,7,Fwhen she was a child.
OL,9,FOn several occasions the jury heard
OL,10,Fabout a letter which Donaldson had
OL,11,Fwritten to A in June 2020. In the
OL,12,Fletter he expressed "regret" for "all
OL,13,Fthe hurt, pain and distress I have
OL,14,Fcaused".
OL,16,FComplainant A told the trial she had
OL,17,Fthought the letter was an attempt "to
OL,18,Fapologise for perhaps the abuse which
OL,19,Fhad occurred".
OL,26,@tD@UOUtD@\O]tD@bOUvD@GO]yD@cOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FDonaldson denied this, stating the
OL,7,Fletter was nothing to do with sexual
OL,8,Fabuse but related to other behaviour.
OL,10,FUnder cross-examination, A was asked
OL,11,Fwhy she had waited until 2024 to make
OL,12,Fher reports alleging the abuse to
OL,13,Fpolice.
OL,15,FShe said: "I knew this would be an
OL,16,Fextremely public affair, involving
OL,17,Fmedia. It was a huge, huge decision."
OL,26,@wD@KOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FWhen a barrister representing Eleanor
OL,7,FDonaldson put it to her that she was
OL,8,F"making this up as you go along", she
OL,9,Fresponded: "I am here to tell the
OL,10,Ftruth."
OL,12,FComplainant B was the next to give
OL,13,Fevidence. She told the jury that she
OL,14,Fremembered two incidents "vividly".
OL,16,FIn one, she claimed that Jeffrey
OL,17,FDonaldson had raped her when she was
OL,18,Fof primary school age.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@`O]qD@LOUrD@GO]vD@ZOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FIn the second incident she claimed
OL,7,Fthat he had touched her when she was
OL,8,Fof secondary school age. She said
OL,9,FEleanor Donaldson had witnessed part
OL,10,Fof this alleged incident but "walked
OL,11,Faway".
OL,13,FWhen challenged during cross-
OL,14,Fexamination about her account, she
OL,15,Fsaid: "Everything I am saying is the
OL,16,Ftruth... no matter how many questions
OL,17,Fpeople ask me it will never change
OL,18,Fthat."
OL,26,@rD@^OUsD@EO]wD@GOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FReferring to her claim of rape, she
OL,7,Fstated: "The actions that night I will
OL,8,Fnever forget, what happened that night
OL,9,Fwill live with me forever."
OL,11,FThe jury next heard from the husband
OL,12,Fof Complainant A who became emotional
OL,13,Fas he told the court about the moment
OL,14,Fhis wife informed him of the abuse
OL,15,Fclaims.
OL,17,FHe said: "She was scared, she had
OL,18,Fnever told anyone this, I recognised
OL,19,Fthis was massive for her."
OL,26,@oD@IOUqD@[O]yD@JOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
