FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FClaire Selfridge, the daughter of
OL,7,FDavid and Linda Hoy, who founded the
OL,8,Fcentre, gave evidence on a video link
OL,9,Ffrom South Africa.
OL,11,FShe told the jury that B told her "she
OL,12,Fhad been abused" in her bedroom.
OL,14,FShe said: "Very shocking, almost like
OL,15,Fa bomb went off, that is what it felt
OL,16,Flike for me."
OL,26,@sD@cOUtD@PO]vD@KOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FThe jury was next played a video of a
OL,7,Fpolice interview with Pastor Stephen
OL,8,FMatthews, who said B had told him in
OL,9,FArmoy about alleged abuse, but asked
OL,10,Fhim not to go to police.
OL,12,FHe said: "She said she can't because
OL,13,Fit would destroy their political
OL,14,Freputation, I don't want that."
OL,16,FMr Matthews said he could not remember
OL,17,Fif B had named her alleged abuser but
OL,18,Fsaid it "became obvious" who it was.
OL,26,@tD@JOUvD@_O]zD@IOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FAsked by a police officer who he
OL,7,Fbelieved that to be, Mr Matthews said:
OL,8,F"There was only one person, that was
OL,9,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson."
OL,11,FDavid and Linda Hoy next appeared as
OL,12,Fwitnesses.
OL,14,FMr Hoy said he had received a phone
OL,15,Fcall from Mr Matthews stating there
OL,16,F"had been an allegation".
OL,18,FHe added: "He said it was against
OL,19,FJeffrey Donaldson."
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@WO]xD@AOUxD@XO]zD@KOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/24
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FMr Hoy arranged the meeting between
OL,7,FDonaldson and Complainant B, which was
OL,8,Falso attended by himself and his wife.
OL,10,FMr Hoy told the jury: "Mr Donaldson
OL,11,Fspoke first, he said I know what this
OL,12,Fis about, he said I am sorry and can
OL,13,Fyou please forgive me."
OL,15,FMr Hoy said he asked B if she wanted
OL,16,Fto "take this any further and she said
OL,17,Fno".
OL,19,FUnder cross-examination, Mr Hoy
OL,20,Fconfirmed no allegations had been
OL,21,Fraised during the short meeting.
OL,26,@rD@WOUuD@WO]xD@DOUyD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/24
