OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FThe audio recordings of police
OL,7,Finterviews with Jeffrey and Eleanor
OL,8,FDonaldson after they were arrested in
OL,9,FMarch 2024 were played to the jury as
OL,10,Fthe trial entered its third week.
OL,12,FWhen asked by a detective about the
OL,13,Fcircumstances of the alleged rape, he
OL,14,Freplied: "I'm sorry, but I can't get
OL,15,Fmy head around this notion."
OL,17,FAsked about the incident in which
OL,18,FComplainant A claimed he had used a
OL,19,Flight to stare at her, Donaldson said:
OL,20,F"I wasn't doing anything untoward."
OL,26,@vD@JOUwD@\O]|D@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G19/24
