OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FHe told police: "I've answered all
OL,7,Fyour questions... I've taken each
OL,8,Fsituation that you've put to me and I
OL,9,Fdo not accept the picture that is
OL,10,Fbeing painted here."
OL,12,FIn her police interview, Eleanor
OL,13,FDonaldson said she was met with a
OL,14,F"blank wall" from her husband when she
OL,15,Frepeatedly asked him about an incident
OL,16,Fin which he had been alone in a room
OL,17,Fwith Complainant B.
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@TO]vD@AOUvD@LO]
