OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FAsked about the claim of rape, she
OL,7,Ftold detectives: "I would say that
OL,8,Fdidn't happen. Absolutely not, oh my
OL,9,Fgoodness."
OL,11,FAsked about the allegations made by
OL,12,Fboth complainants, Eleanor Donaldson
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is a massive, massive
OL,14,Fshock."
OL,16,FJeffrey Donaldson spent two days in
OL,17,Fthe witness box giving evidence, where
OL,18,Fhe repeatedly denied allegations of
OL,19,Fabuse by both women.
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@JO]uD@GOUvD@GO]
