PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782146887
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FHe said he was "crystal clear" that
OL,7,Fthe rape claim is "simply not true".
OL,9,FHe described other claims that he had
OL,10,Fcarried out sexual abuse as "just
OL,11,Funbelievable".
OL,13,FNo other witnesses were called as part
OL,14,Fof his defence.
OL,16,FIn her closing speech, Ms Walsh said
OL,17,Fthere was "no reason" why the two
OL,18,Fwomen would lie about being abused.
