OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson guilty of
OL,4,Chistorical sex offences
OL,6,FShe added: "What the evidence shows
OL,7,Fwhen it is pieced together is that
OL,8,Fthey are telling the truth about what
OL,9,Fhappened to them."
OL,11,FBut Jeffrey Donaldson's barrister
OL,12,FKieran Vaughan KC said in his closing
OL,13,Fspeech there were "significant and
OL,14,Ffundamental issues" with the
OL,15,Fcredibility of each of the
OL,16,Fcomplainants.
OL,18,FHe added: "They are not sufficiently
OL,19,Freliable enough to drive you to a sure
OL,20,Fconclusion that he is guilty."
